ents.\n\n- * You can enjoy various contents of K-POP groups such as performances, music videos,\nmaking films, fan meetings and V-logs etc.\n\n- * You can watch it through streaming service and download content, so you can enjoy\nvideos seamlessly.\n\n- * VR contents of a new K-POP group are uploaded every week.\n\n- * Not only K-POP but also various genres of performance contents will be uploaded.\n\n- * Starflex-VR provides English, Korean and Japanese language setting.\nOther languages also will be serviced in the future\n\n- * If you add Starflex-VR on your \"Wishlist\", you are able to be received updating\nmessage for a new content continuously.", "short_description": "In this platform, you can enjoy various music of K-POP's top idols realistically with s3D VR. Not only\nK-POP but also drama, movie, fan meeting, making film service will be opened. High quality software\nis provided through Multi-Camera system. Please join us. we'll guide you to VR metaverse platform"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://admin.starflexvr.com/privacy.txt", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Starflex-VR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.starflexvr.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["MEDIA_PLAYER", "MUSIC_VIDEO", "MUSIC"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1162243841246565"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}